[INCOMING] {"type":"response.output_item.done","item":{"id":"msg_0b55268b52b92e5e0169dd5c81ba388191bec1fc9fb6f35486","type":"message","status":"completed","content":[{"type":"output_text","annotations":[],"logprobs":[],"text":"```python\ndef quick_sort(arr):\n    if len(arr) <= 1:\n        return arr\n\n    pivot = arr[len(arr) // 2]\n    left = [x for x in arr if x < pivot]\n    middle = [x for x in arr if x == pivot]\n    right = [x for x in arr if x > pivot]\n\n    return quick_sort(left) + middle + quick_sort(right)\n\n\n# 示例\nnums = [5, 3, 8, 4, 2, 7, 1, 10]\nprint(quick_sort(nums))  # [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 7, 8, 10]\n```\n\n如果你想要“原地排序版”（更省内存），我也可以给你。"}],"phase":"final_answer","role":"assistant"},"output_index":1,"sequence_number":179}
